OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry start with sunny spells
OL,6,Ffor many, before increasing cloud
OL,7,Fbrings a small chance of an isolated
OL,8,Flight shower. Conditions are expected
OL,9,Fto remain dry for the vast majority
OL,10,Fthough, with winds continuing to ease.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FAny remaining showers will
OL,13,Ffade away, leaving a largely dry
OL,14,Fevening with light winds. Cloud will
OL,15,Fincrease from the west later, bringing
OL,16,Fa few outbreaks of rain before dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
